last_episode_to_air.name: Fly through a First Order Star Destroyer
last_episode_to_air.overview: Sneak through a First Order Star Destroyer and investigate the corridors and hangar bays walked by legions of loyal stormtroopers and commanded by Supreme Leader Kylo Ren.

name: Star Wars Vehicle Flythroughs
overview: Get up-close-and-personal with some of the Star Wars films’ most iconic and beloved ships and vehicles as this charming series whisks you off for fly-through tours of the Galaxy Far, Far Away.

episodes.name: Fly through the Millennium Falcon
episodes.overview: Come aboard the legendary Millennium Falcon, Star Wars’ iconic smuggler ship flown by the likes of Han Solo, Lando Calrissian, Chewbacca, Rey, and Finn.
